### Allumer la LED
POST http://localhost:8080/devices/light/on

### Éteindre la LED
POST http://localhost:8080/devices/light/off

### Ouvrir la porte
POST http://localhost:8080/devices/door/open

### Fermer la porte
POST http://localhost:8080/devices/door/close


